[
  {
    "startTime": 5.963,
    "endTime": 7.007,
    "text": "Hello, Charlie Brown."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.007,
    "endTime": 11.0,
    "text": "Can your dog come outside to roam aimlessly with me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.0,
    "endTime": 14.139,
    "text": "I'll see if he's available. Snoopy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.139,
    "endTime": 16.933,
    "text": "-Huh? -(kids cheering)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.933,
    "endTime": 18.935,
    "text": "NARRATOR: Welcome to Snoopy's neighborhood."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.935,
    "endTime": 20.561,
    "text": "Prepare to board."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.561,
    "endTime": 22.397,
    "text": "We're already onboard, Captain Sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.397,
    "endTime": 25.857999999999997,
    "text": "NARRATOR: There's so much to see and do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.858,
    "endTime": 27.944,
    "text": "-So let's get started! -Whoo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.944,
    "endTime": 29.238,
    "text": "NARRATOR: First stop, Snoopy's doghouse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.238,
    "endTime": 31.281,
    "text": "It's the ultimate hangout spot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.281,
    "endTime": 35.369,
    "text": "I knew he'd be the talk of the street!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.369,
    "endTime": 38.372,
    "text": "NARRATOR: But only after you've finished your school project."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.372,
    "endTime": 42.75,
    "text": "Ta-da! This is the first time in history"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.75,
    "endTime": 44.419,
    "text": "the Great Golfer Snoopy completed the final hole"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.419,
    "endTime": 48.881,
    "text": "in only 127 shots!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.881,
    "endTime": 49.383,
    "text": "(teacher vocalizing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.383,
    "endTime": 51.009,
    "text": "TOGETHER: C-minus!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.009,
    "endTime": 53.387,
    "text": "-(groans) -Yeah! Whoo-hoo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.387,
    "endTime": 55.472,
    "text": "-(Snoopy panting) -NARRATOR: If things heat up,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.472,
    "endTime": 59.101,
    "text": "go ahead and walk down the street for a dip in the pool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.101,
    "endTime": 62.603,
    "text": "(clamoring)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.603,
    "endTime": 63.771,
    "text": "NARRATOR: Just remember--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.771,
    "endTime": 66.483,
    "text": "No dog germs in the pool!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.483,
    "endTime": 69.902,
    "text": "NARRATOR: Wanna see a movie? Head this way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.902,
    "endTime": 72.863,
    "text": "-(wind howling) -(kids clamoring)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.863,
    "endTime": 73.49,
    "text": "CHARLIE BROWN: You don't like scary movies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.49,
    "endTime": 75.908,
    "text": "(screams)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.908,
    "endTime": 77.785,
    "text": "-(teeth chattering) -Good grief."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.785,
    "endTime": 78.36999999999999,
    "text": "NARRATOR: If it's a breezy day,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.37,
    "endTime": 80.289,
    "text": "it's the perfect time to grab your kite."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.289,
    "endTime": 82.873,
    "text": "I bet the kite-eating tree"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.873,
    "endTime": 84.167,
    "text": "doesn't like its kites pre-chewed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.167,
    "endTime": 86.128,
    "text": "NARRATOR: Just be careful where you fly it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.128,
    "endTime": 89.714,
    "text": "(cries out, grunts)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.714,
    "endTime": 91.757,
    "text": "-(munching) -(sighs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.757,
    "endTime": 92.134,
    "text": "NARRATOR: Or maybe you wanna get a game going"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.134,
    "endTime": 94.969,
    "text": "right here at the baseball field."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.969,
    "endTime": 100.1,
    "text": "Let nothing distract you from this pitch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.1,
    "endTime": 102.18499999999999,
    "text": "But I didn't even throw it yet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.185,
    "endTime": 104.895,
    "text": "NARRATOR: Need to chill out?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.895,
    "endTime": 106.315,
    "text": "Grab your sled and hit the slopes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.315,
    "endTime": 111.944,
    "text": "(cheering)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.944,
    "endTime": 113.821,
    "text": "NARRATOR: And if you can spare a nickel,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.821,
    "endTime": 116.615,
    "text": "there's a place everyone goes for some good advice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.615,
    "endTime": 118.368,
    "text": "We've lost every baseball game so far."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.368,
    "endTime": 121.704,
    "text": "I'm not sure we're ever gonna win one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.704,
    "endTime": 123.58099999999999,
    "text": "Cheer up, Charlie Brown."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.581,
    "endTime": 125.417,
    "text": "-You shouldn't have any doubt. -You think so?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.417,
    "endTime": 128.29500000000002,
    "text": "There's no way your team is ever going to win."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.295,
    "endTime": 130.963,
    "text": "That will be five cents, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.963,
    "endTime": 132.673,
    "text": "(coins clinking)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.673,
    "endTime": 133.467,
    "text": "NARRATOR: Hungry for a snack?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.467,
    "endTime": 137.51100000000002,
    "text": "Go right this way over to Charlie Brown's house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.511,
    "endTime": 140.55599999999998,
    "text": "Oh, boy, blueberry muffins!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.556,
    "endTime": 142.26700000000002,
    "text": "(sniffing) My favorite."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.267,
    "endTime": 144.977,
    "text": "NARRATOR: And that's not all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.977,
    "endTime": 146.854,
    "text": "There's always something to discover"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.854,
    "endTime": 148.73100000000002,
    "text": "in Snoopy's neighborhood."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.731,
    "endTime": 149.316,
    "text": "Come on by and visit anytime."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.316,
    "endTime": 151.776,
    "text": "We'll see you soon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.776,
    "endTime": 152.19400000000002,
    "text": "(clamoring)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.194,
    "endTime": 154.653,
    "text": "-Hey, everyone! -Yeah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.653,
    "endTime": 157.90699999999998,
    "text": "-Hooray! -Can't wait!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.907,
    "endTime": 159.90900000000002,
    "text": "NARRATOR: ...only on Apple TV+."
  }
]